Plinkerton Plonkerton

All player are banished to a seperate room. One by one they do the following:

    1. If you are the first to leave fill a shot glass with water and place a solo cup over it. Otherwise ignore
    2. Fill a shot glass with a drink of your choice and place a solo cup overtop it.
    3. Players can move the cups if they wish, so long as they dont look at the contents of the shot.

Player then return to the room and repeat the steps until all players have gone.
Player then take turns spinning an object in the middle and taking the shot it lands on.

If a player gets the water shot they win the round and get 2pts!
    *Players roll a d20 whoever has the closest point total to the number rolled takes the extra shot.

Players play 3 rounds, if one player wins all 3 round they win a Jackpot!

Jackpot => Allows a player to become effectivly immortal for the duration of a theme song of their choosing.
           While immortal a player can avoid all drinks given to them, except a JORKLE of course.
            *Jackpot theme song may last no longer than 4 minutes and 11 seconds.